thread.title: Pamela Delehanty
thread.title_full: Pixels Logo Design reviewed by Pamela Delehanty

author: Pamela Delehanty
title: Pamela Delehanty
text: I had the most wonderful experience with this company. Their expertise was supreme in the design of my logo. They were very professional with their work ethics by completing each revision in an expeditious manner. They went above and beyond to get the design I had in mind. I would highly recommend them to others and I will most definitely be using them again on future projects.
